<statement>
<p>
Which of the following voting methods will we discuss in this course. Select all that apply!</p>
<p><ol style="list-style-type:upper-alpha"><li>Borda count method</li> 
<li>Plurality method</li> 
<li>Pairwise comparison method</li> 
<li>Hamilton's method</li> 
<li>Plurality with elimination method</li> 
<li>Jefferson's method</li> 
</ol></p>


</statement>
<answer>
<p><ul><li><p>Plurality method</p>
<p>Plurality with elimination method</p>
<p>Borda count method</p>
<p>Pairwise comparison method</p></li></ul></p>
</answer>

